social_posts.post_text: One from a good sesh with friends @tristencooperbmx @ohgjeezy #bmx #cultcrew #ride #bikes
Been falling in love with snowboarding again 🖤 stoked to finally get one of these on film. It’s been a dream to land it since I would get smoked every time I tried as a kid

Having a major Mom brag moment… thanks to @davidpendleton - coaching/videography skills! Not my usual content, but I can’t resist. 

Little known fact about me: I snowboarded professionally in halfpipe during my teen years. I traveled internationally and competed in the Junior World Championships on the US Team alongside future Olympic Gold Medalists @thekellyclark and @gretchenbleiler 
My level of excitement when I saw 

I taught my son, Tage (7), to snowboard a few times on past trips but never made it off the magic carpet, but this trip we put him in lessons to get him on the lift and shredding down the slopes. 
This video, shot by @davidpendleton - who was Tage’s coach on his 2nd half day of snowboard lessons, captured Tage slaying the park - looking like a pro, by the end of the lesson. 

I highly recommend checking out @pendletonproductions for action sport film work and timeless family storytelling videos. David is not only skilled in videography but he is also a FATHER who cares deeply about capturing those special moments 🎥 for families on and off the mountain. 

Thanks for sharing in this gushing moment with me, you know how those proud parent moments go… 🥰
